.TH "get_state_synchronize_rcu" 9 "get_state_synchronize_rcu" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
get_state_synchronize_rcu \- Snapshot current RCU state
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned long" get_state_synchronize_rcu
.BI "(void "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "void" 12
no arguments
.SH "DESCRIPTION"

Returns a cookie that is used by a later call to \fBcond_synchronize_rcu\fP
to determine whether or not a full grace period has elapsed in the
meantime.
